data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is located in the desirable Charleston Square  neighborhood  IN Sandy Springs. Location is so close to the Prado with great shopping and entertainment don't miss you opportunity to enjoy Sandy Springs! FHA Approved it offers easy access to Atlanta's best attractions. This beautiful and cozy home features a large covered back porch. Inside, you'll find a  beautifully updated kitchen with white cabinets, new quartz counters and spacious dining room.
